      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the outline. i really liked the idea of the \"language of luxury\" and the grooming section. can u expand on the grooming part? specifically, what would u say are the core standards for someone to look \"professionally polished\" globally, and then how should they adjust if they are coming from a non-Western background so they don't look out of place?",
